## Attribution

This project is based on [`claude-task-master`](https://github.com/eyaltoledano/claude-task-master) by Eyal Toledano, rebuilt and customized specifically for fiction and narrative projects.

### Key Differences from Original

- **NRD (Novel Requirements Document)** replaces PRD for story outlines
- **Narrative-focused task types**: Acts, chapters, scenes, beats
- **Genre-aware AI prompts** for worldbuilding and character development
- **Manuscript generation** with chapter packets and compiled output

