## MCP Server Configuration

For Cursor integration, add to `.cursor/mcp.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "novel-master-ai": {
      "command": "npx",
      "args": ["-y", "novel-master-ai@latest", "--mcp"],
      "env": {
        "GOOGLE_API_KEY": "your-api-key-here"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

